<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:07:30 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的内容 – 第 156 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-156/0000018e-2946-dbcf-abee-39de37730000</link><description>据报道，埃及正在与哈马斯高级成员和以色列官员接触，以重启停火谈判。 ■ 以色列人质家属将出席联合国安理会有关哈马斯对以色列妇女性暴力的会议。 ■ 730 名以色列学者签署的请愿书呼吁政府“采取紧急措施防止加沙饥饿 ■ 拜登：内塔尼亚胡“对以色列的伤害大于帮助” ■ 战争结束 156 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 18:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-156/0000018e-2946-dbcf-abee-39de37730000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方释放周六晚被拘留的 17 名反政府抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-17-anti-govt-protesters-detained-on-saturday-night/0000018e-292f-d1b8-a5de-e9ff92160000</link><description>一名法官批评警方逮捕一名抗议者，称“在逮捕嫌疑人期间行使自由裁量权是可能的，也许是明智的”，并强调警方没有执行基本的审讯程序</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 17:51:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-release-17-anti-govt-protesters-detained-on-saturday-night/0000018e-292f-d1b8-a5de-e9ff92160000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡回击拜登：如果他的意思是我的政策正在伤害以色列，“他错了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hits-back-at-biden-hes-wrong-if-he-meant-my-policies-are-hurting-israel/0000018e-2955-d1b8-a5de-e9dda8090000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡还攻击了美国旨在重振巴勒斯坦权力机构并反对以色列在拉法采取军事行动的政策目标。 “（以色列）绝大多数人前所未有地团结，”他说</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 17:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-hits-back-at-biden-hes-wrong-if-he-meant-my-policies-are-hurting-israel/0000018e-2955-d1b8-a5de-e9dda8090000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018e-2956-dc52-abff-69d6a8a50000</link><description>中士。一等兵迈克尔·加尔周日在加沙地带南部的战斗中丧生。他于周日晚上被安葬在耶路撒冷的赫茨尔山军事公墓</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 17:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/idf-names-israeli-soldier-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018e-2956-dc52-abff-69d6a8a50000</guid></item><item><title>随着两国关系恶化，内塔尼亚胡指责埃尔多安否认亚美尼亚种族灭绝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publicly-accuses-turkey-of-denying-the-armenian-holocaust/0000018e-287a-d152-ad8e-29fa35a10000</link><description>以色列总理针对土耳其总统将其与希特勒相提并论的表态，标志着两国外交对抗的基调进一步恶化</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 16:36:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-publicly-accuses-turkey-of-denying-the-armenian-holocaust/0000018e-287a-d152-ad8e-29fa35a10000</guid></item><item><title>“贫穷是一件奇怪的事情”：印度新兵并没有因真主党火箭袭击中移民工人的死亡而吓倒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/indian-recruits-undeterred-by-death-of-migrant-worker-in-hezbollah-rocket-attack/0000018e-288d-dbcf-abee-39dda9770000</link><description>印度媒体基本上没有报道尼宾·麦克斯韦尔上周在以色列北部被杀的事件。即使这是头条新闻，也可能不会改变许多前往以色列的建筑工人的想法</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 16:30:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/indian-recruits-undeterred-by-death-of-migrant-worker-in-hezbollah-rocket-attack/0000018e-288d-dbcf-abee-39dda9770000</guid></item><item><title>首席拉比的一句话体现了正统派对战时以色列的傲慢态度</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-rabbi-embodies-haredi-arrogance-toward-needs-of-israeli-society-in-wartime/0000018e-28d7-d152-ad8e-29ff26220000</link><description>塞法迪酋长拉比·伊扎克·约瑟夫（Rabbi Yitzhak Yosef）空洞地威胁犹太学院的学生将离开以色列而不是在军队服役，这是正统派社区历史上的新低</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 16:17:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-rabbi-embodies-haredi-arrogance-toward-needs-of-israeli-society-in-wartime/0000018e-28d7-d152-ad8e-29ff26220000</guid></item><item><title>以色列已经落入哈马斯的陷阱。但还有一条出路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-fallen-into-hamas-trap-but-theres-a-way-out/0000018e-27b9-d152-ad8e-2ff9e7f30000</link><description>哈马斯的希望是刺激以色列杀害足够多的平民，从而在政治上击败以色列——这是以色列已经上当的典型恐怖主义挑衅策略。但击败哈马斯需要非传统思维</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 14:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-10/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-has-fallen-into-hamas-trap-but-theres-a-way-out/0000018e-27b9-d152-ad8e-2ff9e7f30000</guid></item><item><title>应仇视同性恋政党的要求，以色列将 800 万美元用于“犹太身份”纳入国家预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-slips-8-million-for-jewish-identity-at-last-minute-into-state-budget/0000018e-281e-d1b8-a5de-e9de10d30000</link><description>诺姆党请求议会批准追加资金，该资金将用于“促进团结和相互责任，加强对社会和国家的志愿服务精神”以及有关犹太身份问题的“公共外交和广告”等举措</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 12:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-slips-8-million-for-jewish-identity-at-last-minute-into-state-budget/0000018e-281e-d1b8-a5de-e9de10d30000</guid></item><item><title>在所有会议之母上，以色列妇女希望在开创性反战运动的成功基础上再接再厉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</link><description>上周在耶路撒冷举行的一次会议探讨了母性的概念及其在政治组织和激进主义中的作用，团结是当前各种运动（从母亲支持生命到母亲反对暴力）之间的关键目标</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 11:38:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/at-mother-of-all-conferences-israeli-women-look-to-build-on-success-of-anti-war-movement/0000018e-27fa-d1b8-a5de-e7fe07900000</guid></item><item><title>斋月祈祷将于周日在耶路撒冷开始，使加沙战争的紧张局势达到潜在的临界点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</link><description>在政府决定在哈马斯战争期间不再实施新的入境限制后，数千名穆斯林信徒抵达阿克萨/圣殿山大院将使以色列的政策面临考验。</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 10:04:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/ramadan-set-to-begin-in-jerusalem-sunday-bringing-tensions-over-gaza-war-to-peak/0000018e-279b-d152-ad8e-2ffbf5610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列首席塞法迪拉比：如果他们强迫我们参军，我们都会离开这个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</link><description>首席拉比发表上述言论之际，该州向高等法院解释为什么不征召极端正统派男子入伍——尽管豁免他们服役的法律已经到期</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 09:27:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/chief-sephardic-rabbi-if-they-force-us-to-go-to-the-army-well-leave-israel/0000018e-2768-d152-ad8e-2fe86ad80000</guid></item><item><title>考古学家在耶路撒冷附近发现迦南“旭日神庙”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-10/ty-article/archaeologists-discover-canaanite-temple-of-the-rising-sun-in-central-israel/0000018e-26fe-d7d3-abce-66ffa0260000</link><description>这座建于 3,300 年前的纪念性建筑在阿西卡山顶的晨光下闪闪发光，显示出与古埃及的密切文化联系</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 06:44:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-03-10/ty-article/archaeologists-discover-canaanite-temple-of-the-rising-sun-in-central-israel/0000018e-26fe-d7d3-abce-66ffa0260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军命名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-live/biden-there-is-a-red-line-cannot-have-30-000-more-palestinians-dead/0000018e-2684-d152-ad8e-2fece7420000</link><description>以色列国防军点名在加沙战斗中丧生的士兵 ■ 美国总统拜登在 MSNBC 采访中警告称，“不能再有 30,000 名巴勒斯坦人死亡” ■ 美国陆军向加沙派遣船只，运送临时援助港口的物资 ■ 据报道，以色列发动的袭击造成 5 人死亡、9 人受伤在黎巴嫩</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:36:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article-live/biden-there-is-a-red-line-cannot-have-30-000-more-palestinians-dead/0000018e-2684-d152-ad8e-2fece7420000</guid></item><item><title>在没有人质协议的情况下，美国限制以色列在加沙的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/in-absence-of-hostage-deal-u-s-reining-in-israels-actions-in-gaza/0000018e-24e6-dc52-abff-65e6a3230000</link><description>在援助车队事件造成人员伤亡以及以色列政府对阻止援助进入加沙的示威活动不采取行动之后，美国修建海港的计划反映了华盛顿基调的转变。哈马斯无需做出重大让步就能获益，其达成协议的动力可能会下降</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 04:14:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/in-absence-of-hostage-deal-u-s-reining-in-israels-actions-in-gaza/0000018e-24e6-dc52-abff-65e6a3230000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：拉法行动“是一条红线”，内塔尼亚胡“对以色列的伤害大于帮助”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-warns-netanyahu-hurting-israel-more-than-helping-says-he-wants-to-address-knesset/0000018e-25b7-d7d3-abce-65bfc0d40000</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登在发表国情咨文演讲 48 小时后接受 MSNBC 采访时表示，“追击哈马斯不会导致 3 万名巴勒斯坦人死亡，还有其他方法”</description><pubDate>Sun, 10 Mar 2024 00:35:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/biden-warns-netanyahu-hurting-israel-more-than-helping-says-he-wants-to-address-knesset/0000018e-25b7-d7d3-abce-65bfc0d40000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现 18 岁嫌疑人背部中枪，与警方的说法相矛盾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/investigation-finds-18-year-old-suspect-shot-from-the-back-contradicting-polices-version/0000018e-2512-d7d3-abce-65bbd99a0000</link><description>警方调查发现，一名二月份被杀的犯罪嫌疑人背部被连中三枪，这与枪手声称嫌疑人试图用刀袭击他的说法相矛盾，这一说法最初得到了警方的认可</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 23:12:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-10/ty-article/.premium/investigation-finds-18-year-old-suspect-shot-from-the-back-contradicting-polices-version/0000018e-2512-d7d3-abce-65bbd99a0000</guid></item><item><title>数千以色列人抗议政府，警察在特拉维夫使用高压水枪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-govt-police-use-water-cannons-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-24d8-dc52-abff-65da956f0000</link><description>16人在以色列各地举行的反对本杰明·内塔尼亚胡政府的示威活动中被捕，这些示威活动包括海法、贝尔谢巴、凯撒利亚和特拉维夫，抗议者暂时封锁了特拉维夫的阿亚隆高速公路</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 20:42:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-protest-govt-police-use-water-cannons-in-tel-aviv/0000018e-24d8-dc52-abff-65da956f0000</guid></item><item><title>数千人在庆祝国际妇女节时呼吁达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-call-for-a-hostage-deal-while-marking-international-womens-day/0000018e-248d-dbcf-abee-3dddf72e0000</link><description>在特拉维夫人质广场举行的集会上，纪念战争结束 155 天和国际妇女节，希伯来语和阿拉伯语视频强调，“社会无法开始复苏，仍有 134 名男女仍被哈马斯囚禁”</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 19:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/thousands-call-for-a-hostage-deal-while-marking-international-womens-day/0000018e-248d-dbcf-abee-3dddf72e0000</guid></item><item><title>一天之内，以色列各地发生四起枪击事件，造成五人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israelis-shot-dead-in-southern-israel-in-third-shooting-incident-in-one-day/0000018e-24b1-dc52-abff-65b37d020000</link><description>一名男子坐在车里被杀，另外两人在以色列南部城市阿拉德附近的一个加油站被枪杀，一名 33 岁男子在德鲁兹城镇马加尔被枪杀，一名五个孩子的母亲被枪杀海法一家具乐部外</description><pubDate>Sat, 09 Mar 2024 19:52:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-09/ty-article/.premium/two-arab-israelis-shot-dead-in-southern-israel-in-third-shooting-incident-in-one-day/0000018e-24b1-dc52-abff-65b37d020000</guid></item></channel></rss>